com.hcl.voltmx.middleware.api.processor.manager

Interface FoundryRequestManager


  • public interface FoundryRequestManager
    FoundryRequestManager holds different types of handlers to operate on request headers, session, query params and payload. It also holds ServicesManager which can be used to get current executing service info and other service related operations.
    Since:
    Foundry V8 SP3 (8.3)
    See Also:
    ServicesManager, ObjectServicePreProcessor, ObjectServicePostProcessor
